      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI for NIH quantity of interest must be below 10% on the production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 3.1% on the 11.6M-cell production mesh. Iterative residuals converged to 1e-5. Discretization error is well within acceptance criterion."
