      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with sufficient fidelity to reproduce boundary conditions in the CFD model.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro test loop operated at 37°C, blood analog fluid (glycerin-water, viscosity 3.5 cP), inlet/outlet pressures and flow rates logged at 100 Hz. All five operating points replicated in CFD with matching boundary conditions."
