      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples must be representative of the production pump geometry within stated manufacturing tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Three pump specimens from production lot measured by CMM; dimensional deviations within ±0.05 mm of nominal. Mean geometry used as CFD domain. Lot-to-lot variability bounded."
    },
