      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD boundary conditions must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental test conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Inlet flow rates matched to within 0.5% of logged experimental values. Outlet pressure boundary conditions matched to within 1 mmHg. Fluid properties matched to within viscometer measurement uncertainty (±3%). Equivalency confirmed for all five validation operating points."
    }
